<P>Work upon the Ark.</P>
<P>Meditations upon the ARK As a <HI>Type</HI> of the <HI>CHURCH</HI>; Delivered in a SERMON at <HI>Boston,</HI> And now Dedicated unto the Service of <HI>All,</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> especially of those whose Concerns Lye in Ships.</P>
<P>By <HI>Cotton Mather.</HI></P>
